		{
			"name": "Redemptions",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Redeem Prize",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{auth_token}}"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"prizeId\": \"cmgfsbfz90001tm0c37887obt\",\n  \"variantId\": \"cmgfsceoj0003tm0ct54uj47z\",\n  \"addressId\": \"cmgfwfo130001tmnjm7jsq972\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/redemptions/redeem",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"redemptions",
								"redeem"
							]
						},
						"description": "# Redeem Prize\n\nThis endpoint allows users to redeem a prize by providing the prize ID and delivery information. The system will process the redemption request and update the user's balance accordingly.\n\n## Authentication\n\nThis endpoint requires authentication using a Bearer token in the Authorization header.\n\n## Request Body\n\n```json\n{\n  \"prizeId\": \"string\",\n  \"deliveryInfo\": {\n    \"address\": \"string\",\n    \"city\": \"string\",\n    \"state\": \"string\",\n    \"zipCode\": \"string\",\n    \"phone\": \"string\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Request Body Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |\n|-----------|------|----------|-------------|\n| prizeId | string | Yes | The unique identifier of the prize to be redeemed |\n| deliveryInfo | object | Yes | Information about where to deliver the prize |\n| deliveryInfo.address | string | Yes | Street address for delivery |\n| deliveryInfo.city | string | Yes | City name |\n| deliveryInfo.state | string | Yes | State or province code |\n| deliveryInfo.zipCode | string | Yes | Postal/ZIP code |\n| deliveryInfo.phone | string | Yes | Contact phone number with country code |\n\n## Response\n\n### Success Response\n\n**Status Code:** 200 OK\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Prize redeemed successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"redemptionId\": \"string\",\n    \"prizeId\": \"string\",\n    \"status\": \"processing\",\n    \"estimatedDeliveryDate\": \"2023-06-15\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Error Responses\n\n**Status Code:** 400 Bad Request\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Invalid request parameters\",\n  \"errors\": [\n    \"prizeId is required\",\n    \"deliveryInfo.address is required\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Status Code:** 401 Unauthorized\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Authentication required\"\n}\n```\n\n**Status Code:** 403 Forbidden\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Insufficient balance to redeem this prize\"\n}\n```\n\n**Status Code:** 404 Not Found\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Prize not found\"\n}\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- The user must have sufficient balance to redeem the prize\n- All delivery information fields are required\n- Phone number should include country code (e.g., +5511999999999)"
					},
					"response": []
				},
